window.bookSummaryJSON = "Steven James' Christy Award-nominated crime thriller pits FBI Special Agent Bowers against a serial killer who enjoys torturing women. After visiting the mountain vistas where the murderer posed his dead victims, Bowers receives a taunting call from the \"Illusionist.\" Although Bowers gets close, his insidious foe continues to elude him."; 
